                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-35-off185 t18020428-35-cd186"></join>, a silver watch, value 30s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18020428-35-victim271" type="victimName">
                     Philip 
                     Wilkinson
                  <interp inst="t18020428-35-victim271" type="surname" value="Wilkinson"></interp>
